repos.name: 99-reactjs-project-ideas
repos.description: A list of 99 projects anybody interested in learning and understanding moving parts of ReactJS should develop.

repos.description: Real-time beach insights, XAMPP-powered, safety and enjoyment! 🏖️🚀

repos.name: color-background-changer
repos.description: A lightweight web app built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Click a button to instantly change the background color, see the selected color, and experience text color changes in a paragraph. Simple and interactive color exploration.

repos.name: CVWORTH
repos.description: 🤖 AI analysis and tips to enhance your resume.

repos.name: MoneyMagnet
